question: What is the population of Porvoo, Finland as of the end of 2023?
asked_question_translated: Kui suur on Soome Porvoo elanike arv 2023. aasta lõpus?
answer: 2023. aasta lõpus on Soome Porvoo elanike arv ligikaudu 52 000.
answer_translated_eng: At the end of 2023, the population of Porvoo in Finland will be around 52 000.
